      "name": "Hunt Prey",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>The Lyrune-Quah Moon Maiden designates a single creature they can see and hear, or one they're Tracking, as their prey. The Lyrune-Quah Moon Maiden gains a +2 circumstance bonus to Perception checks to @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Seek]{Seek} the prey and to Survival checks to @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Track]{Track} the prey. The multiple attack penalty for attacks against the hunted prey is -3 (-2 with an agile weapon) on the second attack and -6 (-4 with an agile weapon) on the third attack. These effects last until the Lyrune-Quah Moon Maiden uses Hunt Prey again.</p>"
        },
